{
  "stem": "1354.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was bringing some merchandise like fabrics and thread and shoes for the kids, and materials for aprons, for the [? pharmacist. ?] And then he was going to the farm, going from home to home, and selling them this.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And for that he got flour, you know, meat, butter, eggs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that's how we lived there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then, in '42, beginning of '42, came that everybody from that place has to go to Wieliczka.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So what do you do?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You have to obey.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the-- the farmer what we lived there, he took a horse and a buggy and we put in still few things, and we all went to Wieliczka.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Wieliczka-- at that time, my older sister was with us, all my-- Erna, my other sister, she lived that time in Kocmyrzow too.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She didn't-- but she lived separate with her husband, and-- and-- and she had already a baby. '94 this year had that little girl.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyhow, we all went, and they put us over there, I remember, in a big, big, hall.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we didn't know what's waiting for us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were waiting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All of a sudden, after the third day, we see my brother is coming.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he says, I'm looking all over for you for a couple hours.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Don't ask any questions, just come with me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we all had prepared a little bundles, you know, with our personal things, but there was still-- we took some furniture, some other-- other things.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my father says, he didn't realize.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he says, who's going to-- what's going to happen to the things?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So my oldest sister says, I will stay with the things.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
